Everything you need to play 420Gaming DayZ SA - Steam version & modded version!
Everything you need to play PvP Online!
Everything you need to play Battle Royale Online!
Everything you need to play Survival Online!

DayZ SA 0.60.133913 Full Installer

1. Install

2. Run desktop shortcut "DayZ Launcher" to play Online/Offline
	- Click Update, this will check for updates and install them.
	- Click play and Make a selection from the menu.
		- You can direct connect to 420 Gaming Dank DayZ PvP.
		- You can load PvP, BattleRoyale or Survival Online.

Make sure you use the DayZ launcher!
